hello,

first of all thanks for your great api, 

 i just created my own panel to sending msg useing whatsappAPI 

i send text fine and with out problem but when its come to sending audio,image,video code act randomly and send them whenever its feel like to send , 

im useing this code 

        switch ($param) {
          case "text":
            $w->sendMessage($phone, $this->input->post('message'));
            break;
         case "audio":
           $w->sendBroadcastAudio($phone,$this->input->post('audio'));
            break;
            
         case "video":
                $w->sendBroadcastVideo($phone,$this->input->post('video'));
            break;
         case "img":
            $w->sendBroadcastImage($phone,$this->input->post('image'));
            break;
        }

im useing CI and TEXTing work fine but other act randomly .

- im useing windows
- media folder has video but not sending it 
- img sometime only send url with out thumbnail 

can some on give me any tip to make it work stable ?
